== Attack Types ==

=== Sword Attack ===

The primary attack method:
* Forward thrust
* Short range
* Can hit enemies in front
* Damage based on Sword equipped + Level

=== Magic Attack ===

Uses equipped Soul:
* Consumes GEMs
* Range and effect vary by spell
* Can be changed via menu

