== Monster Lairs ==

Key mechanic unique to Soul Blazer:

{| class="wikitable"
! Element !! Function
|-
| Lair || Spawns monsters continuously
|-
| Defeat All || Seals the lair
|-
| Sealed Lair || Releases trapped soul
|-
| Soul || NPC/object returns to world
|}

When all monsters from a lair are defeated:
# Lair seals permanently
# Soul orb appears
# Walk over orb to free soul
# Associated NPC/object restored in town

== Enemy Types ==

=== Basic Enemies ===

* Melee attackers
* Projectile shooters
* Aerial enemies
* Ground crawlers

=== Lair Guardians ===

Some lairs contain stronger enemies or mini-bosses.

=== Area Bosses ===

Each major area has a boss fight:
* Fixed HP
* Attack patterns
* Weak points

== Damage Calculation ==

Damage is based on:
* Attacker's Strength (for player) or Attack (for enemy)
* Defender's Defense
* Equipment bonuses
* Level difference

